{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/introduction-to-arrays-in-javascript/lab-golf-score-translator/build-a-golf-score-translator","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"lab-golf-score-translator","demoType":null,"title":"Napravi prevodilac za golf bodove","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U igri golfa, svaki ručak ima <code>par</code>, što znači prosečan broj <code>strokes</code> koji je golfaš očekivan da postigne kako bi spustio loptu u ručak i završio igru. U zavisnosti od udaljenosti visoko ili nisko od <code>par</code>, tvoji rezultati za <code>strokes</code> imaju drugačije nadimakće.</p>\n<p>U ovoj laboratoriji, ćeš napisati funkciju koja menja <code>par</code> i <code>strokes</code> u njihovo nadimakće.</p>\n<p><strong>Cilj:</strong> Popunite korisničke priče navedene ispod i prođite sve testove kako biste završili laboratorijum.</p>\n<p>Priče o korisniku:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Treba da kreirate funkciju pod nazivom <code>golfScore</code>.</li>\n<li><code>golfScore</code> treba da prihvati dva numerička argumenta: par terena i broj udaraca.</li>\n<li><code>golfScore</code> treba da vrati string.</li>\n<li><code>golfScore</code> treba da vrati <code>\"Hole-in-one!\"</code> ako je <code>strokes</code> jednako <code>1</code>.</li>\n<li><code>golfScore</code> treba da vrati <code>\"Eagle\"</code> ako je <code>strokes</code> manje ili jednako <code>par - 2</code>.</li>\n<li><code>golfScore</code> treba da vrati <code>\"Birdie\"</code> ako je <code>strokes</code> jednako <code>par - 1</code>.</li>\n<li><code>golfScore</code> treba da vrati <code>\"Par\"</code> ako je <code>strokes</code> jednako <code>par</code>.</li>\n<li><code>golfScore</code> treba da vrati <code>\"Bogey\"</code> ako je <code>strokes</code> jednako <code>par + 1</code>.</li>\n<li><code>golfScore</code> treba da vrati <code>\"Double Bogey\"</code> ako je <code>strokes</code> jednako <code>par + 2</code>.</li>\n<li><code>golfScore</code> treba da vrati <code>\"Go Home!\"</code> ako je <code>strokes</code> veće ili jednako <code>par + 3</code>.</li>\n</ol>\n</section>","id":"689f7996426c1534fa5bea66","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":26,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"introduction-to-arrays-in-javascript","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/introduction-to-arrays-in-javascript/lab-golf-score-translator/build-a-golf-score-translator"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"const names = [\"Hole-in-one!\", \"Eagle\", \"Birdie\", \"Par\", \"Bogey\", \"Double Bogey\", \"Go Home!\"];\n","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da kreirate funkciju koja se zove <code>golfScore</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isFunction(golfScore);"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore</code> treba da uzme dva parametra.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf(golfScore, 2);"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore</code> treba da vrati sekvencu slova</p>","testString":"assert.isString(golfScore(4,1)); "},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(1, 1)</code> treba da vrati sekvencu slova <code>Hole-in-one!</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(1,1), 'Hole-in-one!');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(3, 1)</code> treba da vrati sekvencu slova <code>Hole-in-one!</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(3,1), 'Hole-in-one!');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(4, 1)</code> trebalo bi da vrati sekvencu slova <code>Hole-in-one!</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(4,1), 'Hole-in-one!');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(5, 1)</code> bi trebalo da vrati niz slova <code>Hole-in-one!</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(5,1), 'Hole-in-one!');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(4, 2)</code> treba da vrati niz znakova <code>Eagle</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(4,2), 'Eagle');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(5, 2)</code> treba da vrati niz znakova <code>Eagle</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(5,2), 'Eagle');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(3, 2)</code> treba da vrati sekvencu karaktera <code>Birdie</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(3,2), 'Birdie');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(4, 3)</code> treba da vrati sekvencu slova <code>Birdie</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(4,3), 'Birdie');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(5, 4)</code> treba da vrati niz znakova <code>Birdie</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(5,4), 'Birdie');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(3, 3)</code> treba da vrati niz karaktera <code>Par</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(3,3), 'Par');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(4, 4)</code> treba da vrati sekvencu karaktera <code>Par</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(4,4), 'Par');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(5, 5)</code> treba da vrati niz znakova <code>Par</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(5,5), 'Par');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(3, 4)</code> treba vratiti niz znakova <code>Bogey</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(3,4), 'Bogey');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(4, 5)</code> trebalo bi vratiti niz znakova <code>Bogey</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(4,5), 'Bogey');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(5, 6)</code> trebalo bi da vrati niz znakova <code>Bogey</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(5,6), 'Bogey');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(3, 5)</code> trebalo bi da vrati sekvencu karaktera <code>Double Bogey</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(3,5), 'Double Bogey');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(4, 6)</code> trebalo bi da vrati niz znakova <code>Double Bogey</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(4,6), 'Double Bogey');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(5, 7)</code> trebalo bi da vrati sekvencu karaktera <code>Double Bogey</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(5,7), 'Double Bogey');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(3, 7)</code> treba da vrati niz karaktera <code>Go Home!</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(3,7), 'Go Home!');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(4, 8)</code> treba da vrati niz karaktera <code>Go Home!</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(4,8), 'Go Home!');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(5, 9)</code> treba da vrati niz znakova <code>Go Home!</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(golfScore(5,9), 'Go Home!');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/introduction-to-arrays-in-javascript/#lab-golf-score-translator","dashedName":"build-a-golf-score-translator","certification":"introduction-to-arrays-in-javascript","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"introduction-to-arrays-in-javascript","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"lab-golf-score-translator","isFirstStep":true,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/introduction-to-arrays-in-javascript/lecture-working-with-common-array-methods/how-do-you-get-the-index-for-an-element-in-an-array-using-the-indexof-method","prevChallengePath":"/learn/introduction-to-arrays-in-javascript/lab-lunch-picker-program/build-a-lunch-picker-program","id":"689f7996426c1534fa5bea66","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":26,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function golfScore(par, strokes) {\n  if (strokes === 1) {\n    return \"Hole-in-one!\";\n  }\n\n  if (strokes <= par - 2) {\n    return \"Eagle\";\n  }\n\n  if (strokes === par - 1) {\n    return \"Birdie\";\n  }\n\n  if (strokes === par) {\n    return \"Par\";\n  }\n\n  if (strokes === par + 1) {\n    return \"Bogey\";\n  }\n\n  if(strokes === par + 2) {\n    return \"Double Bogey\";\n  }\n\n  return \"Go Home!\";\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/introduction-to-arrays-in-javascript/lab-golf-score-translator/build-a-golf-score-translator"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}